data.description:
Nearly new construction!! This 3 bedroom 2 bath 2 car garage is built by N&B Homes in 2022.
Inside you will find an open floor plan with granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms. This home has beautiful flooring throughout with carpet in the bedrooms. The primary bedroom is isolated with a large closet.  
The backyard has a nice size covered patio perfect for outdoor relaxing along with an automatic sprinkler system.
